Participation Requirements 

Voluntary participation 
2-100 Eligible Employees: A minimum of five employees must enroll (there is not participation-percentage requirement for our voluntary plans). Dual Option is not available for voluntary plans.

Value, Classic, and Enhanced participation 
2-4 Eligible Employees: 100%textNode% of eligible employees (and a minimum of two employees) not covered under another dental plan are required to enroll.

5-100 Eligible Employees: A minimum of 70%textNode% of net eligible employees must enroll for groups size 5 -19. A minimum of 60%textNode% of net eligible employees must enroll for groups sized 20 -100. For orthodontia, a minimum of 5 employees must enroll. Dual Option (employer can select two plan to offer to employees) is available for groups with at least 15 net eligible employees. A minimum of five employees must enroll in each of the two dental plans and the two plans offered must have at least a 10%textNode% premium differential.
